---
title: Service Layer Architecture
description: Service layer architecture with BaseCrudService pattern
author: Tech Team
date: 2025-11-06
---

```mermaid
graph TD
    %% Base Service
    BaseService[🎯 BaseCrudService<T><br/>Abstract Base Class]

    %% Base Properties
    subgraph BaseProperties[Base Properties]
        Context[🔐 ctx: ServiceContext<br/>- actor: Actor<br/>- requestId: string]
        Model[🗃️ model: BaseModel<T>]
        Logger[📝 logger: Logger]
    end

    %% Base Methods
    subgraph BaseMethods[Base CRUD Methods]
        Create[➕ create input<br/>→ ServiceOutput<T>]
        FindById[🔍 findById id<br/>→ ServiceOutput<T>]
        FindAll[📋 findAll filters<br/>→ ServiceOutput<T[]>]
        Update[✏️ update id, data<br/>→ ServiceOutput<T>]
        SoftDelete[🗑️ softDelete id<br/>→ ServiceOutput<void>]
        HardDelete[❌ hardDelete id<br/>→ ServiceOutput<void>]
        Restore[♻️ restore id<br/>→ ServiceOutput<T>]
    end

    %% Helper Methods
    subgraph HelperMethods[Helper Methods]
        RunWithLogging[🔧 runWithLoggingAndValidation<br/>- Validate input Zod<br/>- Log operation<br/>- Handle errors<br/>- Return ServiceOutput]
        CheckPermissions[🔒 checkPermissions<br/>- Verify actor permissions<br/>- Throw FORBIDDEN]
    end

    %% Concrete Services
    AccommodationService[🏠 AccommodationService<br/>extends BaseCrudService]
    DestinationService[📍 DestinationService<br/>extends BaseCrudService]
    EventService[🎉 EventService<br/>extends BaseCrudService]
    PostService[📰 PostService<br/>extends BaseCrudService]
    UserService[👤 UserService<br/>extends BaseCrudService]
    ReviewService[⭐ ReviewService<br/>extends BaseCrudService]
    SubscriptionService[💳 SubscriptionService<br/>extends BaseCrudService]
    PurchaseService[🛒 PurchaseService<br/>extends BaseCrudService]
    PricingTierService[💰 PricingTierService<br/>extends BaseCrudService]

    %% Custom Methods Examples
    subgraph AccommodationCustom[Accommodation Custom Methods]
        SearchAccommodations[🔍 searchAccommodations<br/>- Full-text search<br/>- Filters: city, price<br/>- Pagination]
        GetFeatured[⭐ getFeaturedAccommodations<br/>- Filter by featured<br/>- Sort by rating]
        CheckAvailability[📅 checkAvailability<br/>- Date range check<br/>- Return boolean]
    end

    subgraph SubscriptionCustom[Subscription Custom Methods]
        Subscribe[➕ subscribe<br/>- Create subscription<br/>- Process payment<br/>- Activate features]
        Cancel[❌ cancel<br/>- Cancel subscription<br/>- Update billing<br/>- Deactivate features]
        Renew[🔄 renew<br/>- Renew subscription<br/>- Charge payment<br/>- Extend period]
    end

    subgraph PurchaseCustom[Purchase Custom Methods]
        ProcessPayment[💳 processPayment<br/>- Validate payment<br/>- Create transaction<br/>- Update status]
        RefundPayment[↩️ refundPayment<br/>- Process refund<br/>- Update transaction<br/>- Notify user]
    end

    %% Service Context Flow
    APIRequest[🔌 API Request]
    CreateContext[🔐 Create ServiceContext<br/>- Extract actor from JWT<br/>- Generate requestId]
    InstantiateService[⚙️ Instantiate Service<br/>new XxxService ctx]
    CallMethod[📞 Call Service Method<br/>service.create data]

    %% Internal Flow
    ValidateInput[✅ Validate Input<br/>Zod Schema]
    CheckPerms[🔒 Check Permissions<br/>Actor + Resource]
    CallModel[🗃️ Call Model Method<br/>model.create data]
    HandleResult[📦 Handle Result<br/>Transform to ServiceOutput]
    ReturnOutput[📤 Return ServiceOutput<br/>success + data/error]

    %% Service Output
    subgraph ServiceOutput[ServiceOutput<T>]
        SuccessPath[✅ Success Path<br/>success: true<br/>data: T]
        ErrorPath[❌ Error Path<br/>success: false<br/>error: ServiceError]
    end

    %% Relationships
    BaseService --> BaseProperties
    BaseService --> BaseMethods
    BaseService --> HelperMethods

    BaseService -.->|extends| AccommodationService
    BaseService -.->|extends| DestinationService
    BaseService -.->|extends| EventService
    BaseService -.->|extends| PostService
    BaseService -.->|extends| UserService
    BaseService -.->|extends| ReviewService
    BaseService -.->|extends| SubscriptionService
    BaseService -.->|extends| PurchaseService
    BaseService -.->|extends| PricingTierService

    AccommodationService --> AccommodationCustom
    SubscriptionService --> SubscriptionCustom
    PurchaseService --> PurchaseCustom

    %% Flow
    APIRequest --> CreateContext
    CreateContext --> InstantiateService
    InstantiateService --> CallMethod
    CallMethod --> ValidateInput
    ValidateInput --> CheckPerms
    CheckPerms --> CallModel
    CallModel --> HandleResult
    HandleResult --> ReturnOutput
    ReturnOutput --> ServiceOutput

    ServiceOutput --> SuccessPath
    ServiceOutput --> ErrorPath

    %% Error Handling
    ValidateInput -.->|Invalid| ErrorPath
    CheckPerms -.->|Forbidden| ErrorPath
    CallModel -.->|DB Error| ErrorPath
    HandleResult -.->|Business Logic Error| ErrorPath

    %% Styling
    classDef base fill:#1e293b,stroke:#0f172a,color:#fff
    classDef properties fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1e40af,color:#fff
    classDef methods fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff
    classDef helpers fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,color:#fff
    classDef concrete fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#fff
    classDef custom fill:#ec4899,stroke:#db2777,color:#fff
    classDef flow fill:#06b6d4,stroke:#0891b2,color:#fff
    classDef output fill:#22c55e,stroke:#16a34a,color:#fff
    classDef error fill:#ef4444,stroke:#dc2626,color:#fff

    class BaseService base
    class Context,Model,Logger properties
    class Create,FindById,FindAll,Update,SoftDelete,HardDelete,Restore methods
    class RunWithLogging,CheckPermissions helpers
    class AccommodationService,DestinationService,EventService,PostService,UserService,ReviewService,SubscriptionService,PurchaseService,PricingTierService concrete
    class SearchAccommodations,GetFeatured,CheckAvailability,Subscribe,Cancel,Renew,ProcessPayment,RefundPayment custom
    class APIRequest,CreateContext,InstantiateService,CallMethod,ValidateInput,CheckPerms,CallModel,HandleResult,ReturnOutput flow
    class SuccessPath output
    class ErrorPath error
```
